        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Obtains a picture from a pool if any is immediately available.</para>
<para>The picture must be released with <ref refid="vlc__picture_8h_1ac6d35f6432c90cfbe6d0aa93759bed5a" kindref="member">picture_Release()</ref>.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>a picture, or NULL if all pictures in the pool are allocated</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>This function is thread-safe. </para>
